profile:
Visit euroyardservice.com for the ULTIMATE service experience...

 Enjoy 100% risk free experience! We want you to be totally thrilled
with our service. So absolutely delighted you will recommend us to your
friends and neighbours. Frankly, we want to take care of your property
forever. You are the judge, if our work is not excellent, we will re-do
the item in question for FREE. If you are still not happy, you will not
owe us one red dime.

There's more! If the item in question is not fixed to your total
satisfaction we will pay another company of your choice to fix the issue.
Nothing is more important to us than your complete satisfaction.

About us: Euro Yard Service has been in the business of helping homeowners maintain beautiful landscapes in the Edmonton area for over 7 years. We have the strongest guarantee in the area… GUARANTEED!

Services Offered: Lawn Maintenance, Spring Cleanup, Fall Cleanup, Power Raking, Aeration,  Snow Removal, Lawn Installation and Renovation, Fertilization, Tree Services, Shrub Care, Eaves Trough Cleaning & more...

Service Areas: Edmonton (West and South-West), Spruce Grove, Stony Plain & Parkland County

10.5 Reasons Why You Should Choose Us Over the Other Guys: 

• OUR 100% NO RISK GUARANTEE... means absolutely 100% NO RISK to try us.
• WE HAVE RAVING CLIENTS… Just look at our testimonials!
• WE SHOW UP WHEN WE SAY… if we don't...we'll notify you before
• YOU CAN CALL US ANYTIME… 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. 
• WE PROTECT YOUR PROPERTY… with our $2,000,000.00 insurance policy.
• WE CARE ABOUT THE DETAILS… and clean up after every visit
• WE SPEAK ENGLISH… All employees are fluent English speaking  
• WE SCREEN OUR EMPLOYEES… Everyone employee goes through a thorough background check.
• WE CARRY WORKERS COMP… If an employee is injured on your property, it's covered.
• WE ARE PASSIONATE ABOUT OUR WORK… our workers love to showcase our clients properties
• WE HAVE 15+ YEARS EXPERIENCE… and are privately owned!
